Londen mr. r. Pindan
sence Iwrott you last non fian you, according bo my romise rave
desired m. Solles to pay £7:14„8½ st att 35:2 for the ballace
of yd acctt which le will also deliver you, & my order m
seaman for £23„6:8 fle which is not altogheter £18 t
for I have sence seenred some gloves of his, by which the debe
en so pmuch the less, & shis is all I could do in yds behalf fo
blease to give m. Collus a full discharge for mee, ar s have sand
JJ understand that seaman is sall on Eng
London m. Aen Loyd
sence mine to you of tle 17 past reed. yd of 173d. I donst
quission butt that you save placed the bale of by tes you receaved
fiam aboard warner, to yd acctt. according to the invoye chersent
if yon pleases to have any more, give mee yds orders, & o dout
ont do all the rest in cheaness, then never medele with any more
for I am sure I can have y upon the ven best termes
because of great bussynes of late could not send you the acct
of the vearre & almonds desiree, but shall make them up
first, I am promised the tykes next week for the yeame, & shall
send you thim, In the meane while I finde wee fave a quich
demand for 22 bite lace for Eng. & I lave made itt mill my bestes
to buy that comt & finde my commissions in ercase sene 2 yead
so that I doubt not butt mij freinds finde their gals. vere well
as they told nue that of late where bere, & I could not butt
accqhant you with this in case you would undertake tlat trade
Dam of opinnon you will menage itt better, or as well as any the
I know, & if you will omploy meeesou may make a dryall, & belaw
mee I'll doo all Jcan to give contene

Putss dopen desen 9 July 1682
e confieur in antwort vanden uwen in 6 deser is ons godt heden gdarrivedrt
soo ingevalle ul gelieft over te comen ul sal mij willeom wesen, ick hebbe
bods carsdy en coit on voy frisads en ander goot daer mode ontfangen
sal voor ul 6 seradre bayen uyt gouden tot ul ordrcomst, al soo ick
fder gddrue ul selfs gier sal sien, op dat ul sijn contens dmd bsde

Rntdos 139 Guldt 1682
mons en rispons ie bien vdodu los vostors du rot t8 u vous os ay crodite vouv la
cullour de 27½ a de dantilles, que vous m'abez anvoyez. tous chant le messagdiro
du suen di 12 ost afsoul dindes bidn requss, la raison qui n'abidez pas en cor 5d
no bollos d'arritement a ndupoot de vostre pac quettes de 28 passato, acco
qui du du purs n'avons pas u le lettres des englogovod, avoc sos quelles mons
de balliogo est ordinaire mens accoutume descrir, non obstants qui ie suis bide
assadri que ls pacquage qui nous onvoyous E& van di ost delivoid en mou port
dibout he wjnde pour pardir alovo comme colles de beudredy partent ls dimanch
ou soir de m'uport comme vous out vouvevez toutsiouvo. ie voy qui vous
in anvoy drez pour de main ofvois ou quatoes parquettey ie me man quevay pas
de proudvs bon coin aff in qui ne savons de porge fons faute sur quoy vous pouvie
oft ve asseures poue puis qui ie suis e base E maine a
noupoort michiel de vallicgo
Antswerpen desen 10 July 1682
Conse bij den uwen van 8 deser sien dat den mijnen van 3 du 6 ditto met de
bij gaende pacqudttions was geworden, als oock den van 29 passato, gops Jet dobbel
prchottien als dan voor d'ordre van mons antgoui roussiau ul sodgesonden mode hebt
ontfangen, al godsdl ul daer over geen montie maecht, ende monsr roussiau mj
gistdven adviseert van 't selve nocg niets hadt & nomen, heden soude aen ul per bodd
guilliam van ardenborgh den rackettien met addres aen tel, bstaende van 4 duchdle
waer van t minste frant gadt en voor d'anddre 3t port gelieft te betaelen
volgende dordre van monsvantfou voussiau voors van brussel waer mede naer
grodtinisse blijve
